 critical scenarios and,\nconsequently, the performance at system level as well. Through extensive\nnumerical simulations, we show that the proposed GSA provides a significant\nperformance improvement with respect to the legacy random scheduling.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 Apr 2018 09:18:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-04-19"}
