ics than the RAFOS floats, replicate the main\naspects of the Lagrangian geography. Finally, consistency with independent\nresults from a chemical tracer release experiment is found to provide\nadditional support to the results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 Apr 2018 02:57:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-20"}
